window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>I’ve been in hiding for four years. On the run from the man in whose bed I once slept. </p> <p>I saw something I shouldn’t have seen. Took something I shouldn’t have taken. And he’s just found me. </p> <p>But it’s not just my safety I have to worry about. I have a little boy. <i>His</i> little boy. The secret baby of a Russian mobster. </p> <p>He told me in no uncertain terms that I’m his. That we would be a family. </p> <p>But his uncle still wants me dead, and I know the man who's been hunting me is the only one who can keep us safe. </p>"; 
